          - rid: 107151359355650177
          output: It seems the artist's faith transcends the need for sectarian ties.
            He remains content to paint the Beholder and little else. We heard he
            told the messengers of other folds that "his faith would be decided at
            the next Faith Eclipse."
        - weight: 50
